{"id":232873282,"title":"一分鐘呼吸法百日修煉 #星誌73","content":"我將從今天開始每天晚上10點修煉一分鐘呼吸法連續一百天！每次修煉十一分鐘\n\n歡迎大家在每天晚上10點加入我的修煉行列！\n\n修煉時間：\n1/11-4/19 22:00-22:11\n\n一分鐘呼吸法修煉方式：\n\n吸氣20秒\n閉氣20秒\n吐氣20秒\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/KuwPJIi.jpg\n\n這裡有一分鐘呼吸法的說明及相關文章：\nhttp://kundaliniparamnam.blogspot.com/2014/04/blog-post_7.html?m=1\n\nhttp://moonshinetigs.blogspot.com/2018/11/blog-post.html?m=1\n\nhttps://kknews.cc/health/z3ejv2l.amp\n\n我推薦大家下載節拍器App，在進行一分鐘呼吸法時把節拍調成一拍=30(代表一分鐘敲30下=2秒敲一下)這樣就可以精準的計算呼吸長度及呼吸次數！\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/xXJ5ZLI.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/P6jrryA.png\n\n設定一拍=30 \n敲10下 吸氣\n敲10下 閉氣\n敲10下 吐氣\n\n建議大家在晚上10點開始修煉呼吸法前先唱一段聖歌：\n\nOng Namo Guru Dev Namo\n\n上面這個歌詞反覆唱三次就OK! \n\n這是這首聖歌的音樂：\nhttps://youtu.be/DPv7poVriBk\n\n這是這首聖歌的相關文章：\nhttp://kundaliniparamnam.blogspot.com/2014/05/ong-namo-guru-dev-namo.html?m=1\n\nhttps://kknews.cc/regimen/a8y6eex.amp\n\n修煉完後依照昆達里尼瑜珈的傳統就是唸三次 Satnam(梵文) ，就是真實的自我的意思。\n\n祝大家修煉愉快！","excerpt":"我將從今天開始每天晚上10點修煉一分鐘呼吸法連續一百天！每次修煉十一分鐘，歡迎大家在每天晚上10點加入我的修煉行列！，修煉時間：1/11-4/19 22：00-22：11，一分鐘呼吸法修煉方式：吸氣2","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"37a78696-f6a6-48ec-a19f-688f799a2aed","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-11T15:43:25.825Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-11T15:44:31.644Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":17,"tags":[],"topics":["呼吸","修煉","冥想","星門日誌","光的勝利"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"靈異","forumAlias":"marvel","school":"逢甲大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":16},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/KuwPJIi.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/xXJ5ZLI.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/P6jrryA.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"493afae8-f4b2-4b99-ad7e-65cf03a